{"tid":1876750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"感謝藍絲親戚激發我戰鬥力","createTime":"2020-02-12T15:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T15:02:38.000Z","uid":270181,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"980ffe2d37514b1fa3a99dbdab818e4698213dfe","tid":1876750,"uid":270181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"我經過幾次試買口罩，<br />\n然後連網都入唔到嘅經驗後，<br />\n已經對上網同人鬥快搶口罩失去戰鬥力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我本身都無打算去眾志網試下同人搶。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係</span></span>，<br />\n今日我媽返到屋企（我媽都係黃），<br />\n同我講班藍撚親戚今晚會上眾志個網試搶口罩，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">雖則要比錢買，<br />\n但我認為嚟班仆街唔配有眾志爭取返嚟嘅口罩。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我決定 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搶口罩</span> <br />\n(其實我屋企都差不多無了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但我重點比較唔想佢哋班藍撚搶到。<br />\n<br />\n結果<br />\n各位，<br />\n我經過多次嘅失敗後，<br />\n今次成功買到一盒口罩！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但令我最高興嘅事係，<br />\n班藍撚親戚一盒都買唔到！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />媽爸，我終於成功買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}